where I married your father.

597
01:19:31,585 --> 01:19:34,233
You love the water.
It'll be beautiful in May.

598
01:19:35,193 --> 01:19:37,111
Didn't you hear what I said?

599
01:19:38,237 --> 01:19:39,822
What's your name?

600
01:19:42,200 --> 01:19:43,534
Where's your mother?

601
