what you're gonna look like.

626
01:22:17,855 --> 01:22:19,482
I love you, Sean.

627
01:22:36,833 --> 01:22:38,417
I'm not Sean.

628
01:23:07,071 --> 01:23:08,781
I'm not Sean.

629
01:23:09,907 --> 01:23:11,868
Because I love you.

630
