660
01:27:41,053 --> 01:27:42,555
I wanna be with you.

661
01:27:44,557 --> 01:27:45,892
Yes, I do.

662
01:27:50,021 --> 01:27:51,981
And I wanna get married.

663
01:27:52,085 --> 01:27:53,357
And...

664
01:27:55,234 --> 01:27:58,654
I wanna have a good life,
